# Review Gate

Before delivering ANY code, run through ALL 5 gates in `.ai-suite/workflows/review-gate.md`:

1. Security gate (10 questions) — BLOCKING if any item fails
2. Quality gate (10 questions)
3. Testing gate (10 questions)
4. Performance gate (5 questions)
5. Documentation gate (5 questions)

If any gate item fails:
- Flag it to the user explicitly
- Explain the risk
- Propose a fix
- NEVER silently skip a failed item
